#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.uniform"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a uniform distribution."
msgstr "从均匀分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are uniformly distributed over the half-open interval ``[low, "
"high)`` (includes low, but excludes high).  In other words, any value "
"within the given interval is equally likely to be drawn by `uniform`."
msgstr ""
"样本在半开区间 ``[low, high)``（包括 low，但不包括 high）上均匀分布。"
"换句话说，给定区间内的任何值被 `uniform` 抽取的可能性相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:8 of
msgid ""
"Lower boundary of the output interval.  All values generated will be "
"greater than or equal to low.  The default value is 0."
msgstr "输出区间的下界。所有生成的值都将大于或等于 low。默认值为 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:11 of
msgid ""
"Upper boundary of the output interval.  All values generated will be less"
" than high.  The default value is 1.0."
msgstr "输出区间的上界。所有生成的值都将小于 high。默认值为 1.0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:14 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``low`` and ``high`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``mt.broadcast(low, high).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状为，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），且 ``low`` 和 ``high`` 都是标量，则"
"返回单个值。否则抽取 ``mt.broadcast(low, high).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:19 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:21 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:23 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:26 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized uniform distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的均匀分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`randint`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:32 of
msgid "Discrete uniform distribution, yielding integers."
msgstr "离散均匀分布，生成整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`random_integers`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:35 of
msgid "Discrete uniform distribution over the closed interval ``[low, high]``."
msgstr "在闭区间 ``[low, high]`` 上的离散均匀分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:37 of
msgid ":py:obj:`random_sample`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:38 of
msgid "Floats uniformly distributed over ``[0, 1)``."
msgstr "在 ``[0, 1)`` 上均匀分布的浮点数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:40 of
msgid ":py:obj:`random`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:41 of
msgid "Alias for `random_sample`."
msgstr "`random_sample` 的别名。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:43 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rand`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:44 of
msgid ""
"Convenience function that accepts dimensions as input, e.g., "
"``rand(2,2)`` would generate a 2-by-2 array of floats, uniformly "
"distributed over ``[0, 1)``."
msgstr ""
"便捷函数，接受维度作为输入，例如 ``rand(2,2)`` 会生成一个 2x2 的浮点数组"
"，均匀分布在 ``[0, 1)`` 上。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:47 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:48 of
msgid "The probability density function of the uniform distribution is"
msgstr "均匀分布的概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:50 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"p(x) = \\frac{1}{b - a}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:52 of
msgid "anywhere within the interval ``[a, b)``, and zero elsewhere."
msgstr "在区间 ``[a, b)`` 内任意位置为该值，其它位置为零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:54 of
msgid ""
"When ``high`` == ``low``, values of ``low`` will be returned. If ``high``"
" < ``low``, the results are officially undefined and may eventually raise"
" an error, i.e. do not rely on this function to behave when passed "
"arguments satisfying that inequality condition."
msgstr ""
"当 ``high`` == ``low`` 时，将返回 ``low`` 的值。如果 ``high`` < ``low``，"
"结果未定义，并可能最终引发错误，即不要依赖该函数在传入满足此不等式条件的"
"参数时的行为。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:61 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:62 of
msgid "Draw samples from the distribution:"
msgstr "从分布中抽取样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:68 of
msgid "All values are within the given interval:"
msgstr "所有值都在给定区间内："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.uniform.uniform:75 of
msgid ""
"Display the histogram of the samples, along with the probability density "
"function:"
msgstr "显示样本的直方图以及概率密度函数："

